OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1774890348
OL,3,CCardiff City loses #100m compensation
OL,4,Cclaim over Emiliano Sala
OL,6,FCardiff City's claim for more than
OL,7,F#100 million in compensation after the
OL,8,Fdeath of footballer Emiliano Sala has
OL,9,Fbeen dismissed by a court in France.
OL,11,FThe football club was claiming against
OL,12,FNantes for loss of income and other
OL,13,Fdamages after the Argentinian striker
OL,14,Fdied in a plane carrying him across
OL,15,Fthe English Channel in 2019. Both he
OL,16,Fand pilot David Ibbotson were killed
OL,17,Fin the crash off the coast of Alderney.
OL,19,FSala, 28, had recently left French
OL,20,Fside FC Nantes to join Cardiff City in
OL,21,Fa #15 million transfer.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
