FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1774890348
OL,3,CCardiff City loses #100m compensation
OL,4,Cclaim over Emiliano Sala
OL,6,FIn 2022, an inquest into Sala's death
OL,7,Ffound he had died of head and chest
OL,8,Finjuries but would have been
OL,9,Funconscious at the time of the crash
OL,10,Fdue to carbon monoxide poisoning.
OL,12,FThree years ago, Cardiff City
OL,13,Fconfirmed it had finished paying FC
OL,14,FNantes that multi-million transfer fee
OL,15,Fbut said it intended to continue its
OL,16,Flegal action in the French courts.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
