OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1774890348
OL,3,CCardiff City loses #100m compensation
OL,4,Cclaim over Emiliano Sala
OL,6,FThe Welsh club had claimed Nantes was
OL,7,Fresponsible because the flight had
OL,8,Fbeen organised by football agent
OL,9,FWilliam "Willie" McKay, who was
OL,10,Fenlisted by the French club.
OL,12,FHowever the Tribunal de Commerce de
OL,13,FNantes ruled that FC Nantes were not
OL,14,Fliable for negligence over Sala's
OL,15,Fdeath.
OL,26,@qD@IOUqD@PO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
