FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1774890348
OL,3,CCardiff City loses #100m compensation
OL,4,Cclaim over Emiliano Sala
OL,6,FCardiff have been ordered to pay
OL,7,FNantes 300,000 euros in damages, and
OL,8,Fan additional 180,000 euros ` coming
OL,9,Fto a total sum of 480,000 euros
OL,10,F(#416,594), a lawyer for the Welsh
OL,11,Fclub said.
OL,13,FA statement issued by Cardiff FC on
OL,14,FMonday read: "We deeply regret that
OL,15,Fthe court did not recognise FC Nantes'
OL,16,Fliability in this tragedy.
OL,18,F"We initiated these proceedings so
OL,19,Fthat the full truth of this case could
OL,20,Fcome to light, in respect of Emiliano
OL,21,FSala's memory.
OL,26,@vD@NOUzD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1774890348
OL,3,CCardiff City loses #100m compensation
OL,4,Cclaim over Emiliano Sala
OL,6,F"How is it possible that, in the end,
OL,7,FFC Nantes - which never contributed to
OL,8,Fthe support fund we launched in memory
OL,9,Fof Emiliano - paid more money to
OL,10,FWillie McKay (1.5 million euros) than
OL,11,Fto the Sala family?
OL,13,F"More than ever, there is an urgent
OL,14,Fneed to strengthen safety and ethical
OL,15,Fstandards in the management and
OL,16,Fprotection of players, so that such a
OL,17,Ftragedy can never happen again.
OL,19,F"The world of football must take a
OL,20,Fhard look at itself."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU{D@AOU|D@UO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/7
