OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1774890348
OL,3,CCardiff City loses #100m compensation
OL,4,Cclaim over Emiliano Sala
OL,6,FIn 2021, businessman David Henderson
OL,7,Fwas jailed for 18 months after he was
OL,8,Fconvicted of endangering the safety of
OL,9,Fthe aircraft, after a trial at Cardiff
OL,10,FCrown Court.
OL,12,FHe had also pleaded guilty to another
OL,13,Fcharge of trying to arrange a flight
OL,14,Ffor a passenger without permission or
OL,15,Fauthorisation.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/7
